{"tid":1666510,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理Post] 過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T09:37:35.000Z","uid":319235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eade9bf2750483020587a760c610cac4a302988a","tid":1666510,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"生存喺平行時空嘅人，緊係乜都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKOneResp/videos/655914578268551/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKOneResp%2Fvideos%2F655914578268551%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=b27dd4ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKOneResp/videos/655914578268551/</a><br />\n<br />\nFB有Page搞緊個意見收集<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=eee81bab\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a><br />\n雖然區議員候選人可以唔答／無視，不過唔係個個香港人都會識睇連登架嘛，推個post出嚟，share比D中佬同港豬，比佢地知佢地究竟投緊比D乜人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原文：<br />\n2019年區議會選舉將至，為了更了解候選人的理念，「有種責任」決定向各候選人以電郵方式發問。所有問題都會以匿名形式記錄，歡迎大家留下問題，我們會代為發問。<br />\n<br />\n所有收集所得的資料會在選舉後一個月內刪除，不會轉讓給第三方人士。<br />\n<br />\n關於我們：敝平台「有種責任」並非主流傳媒，僅由數名關心香港的「九十後」青年於今年6月開立，並於在不同的網上平台包括：Facebook、YouTube、Instagram及Telegram，向市民發佈新聞資訊。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何疑問，歡迎以電郵方式聯絡。謝謝！<br />\n電郵地址：HKOneResp@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n歡迎Share出去，讓更多人提供問題。<br />\n截止日期：2019年10月31日"},{"pid":"211d26c7d5e1ef706546a771d30452048fc771f4","tid":1666510,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 21<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>12:30 醫民同行 醫護抗暴 靜坐行動</strong></span> <br />\n- 八間醫院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:00 - 23:00 毋忘721 元朗恐襲三個月靜坐</strong></span><br />\n- 18區黨鐵站大堂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>#39mRunFor721 全港和理跑</strong></span><br />\n- [時間地點不限 跑步計時39分鐘]"},{"pid":"35ea51e5d1cc433898bbbde1b7566f68b70121eb","tid":1666510,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"c09919e1b71d8d1e363c848bc08a9feac285d6d2","tid":1666510,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abfb050147d7309851fa2a2ee18f0c68e2d4b4e","tid":1666510,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"推多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae87cbc5f38253c706048d8650a348cea0becc3d","tid":1666510,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVqbJxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVqbJxu.png&h=a933631f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果有嘢幫到手即管開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c13eb8e86c1ac27a07cf868e5c0df8616336fe1","tid":1666510,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"cc922a26f89af71a6b0b781d37c2755bb9052239","tid":1666510,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae87cbc5f38253c706048d8650a348cea0becc3d","tid":1666510,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVqbJxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVqbJxu.png&h=a933631f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果有嘢幫到手即管開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662979/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662979/page/1</a><br />\n要貼埋link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406d9ed12ffbc2a825f5008d00d4b87f33e4fb02","tid":1666510,"uid":28845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"又係呢條臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1db4f9e5fd7133b75ab97dc7f33d355e6edadc","tid":1666510,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"eb9a2339a3f0e4439403b9af8fc7a9d665494d03","tid":1666510,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"樓主收集到幾多問題?"}]}